	<!-- AboutActivity -->
	<string name="overview_label">Overview</string>
	<string name="about_overview1">
		Bomb Squad is a cooperative board game where 2-6 players are members of a team,
		operating a disposal robot with the mission to disarm bombs and save hostages.
		The players work together, racing against the clock to provide the appropriate
		instructions for the robot to achieve their mission objectives.
	</string>
	<string name="about_overview2">
		This app is used along with the physical board game to manage the bomb timers
		counting down during a mission, to help the players with the setup for each building
		and mission in the game\'s Campaign mode, and also is used to stop the timers for
		individual bombs when those bombs are successfully disarmed in time.  In addition,
		we\'ve found that the app significantly enhances the game experience and makes that
		tension of bombs counting down feel more real as you play the game.  We hope you
		enjoy it as much as we do!
	</string>
